@startuml sequence_tenant_resolution
!theme plain
skinparam sequenceMessageAlign center

title Tenant Resolution - Happy Path + Failure Cases

participant "HTTP Request" as Req
participant "JwtBearerMiddleware" as JWT
participant "TenantContextMiddleware" as TCM
participant "IUserBlacklist" as BL
database "Users / UserOrganization" as DB
participant "ITenantContext" as Ctx
participant "Controller" as Ctrl

== Happy Path ==

Req -> JWT: Authorization: Bearer <token>
JWT -> JWT: Validate signature, issuer, audience
JWT -> TCM: Authenticated ClaimsPrincipal

TCM -> TCM: Extract EntraObjectId from claims
TCM -> BL: IsBlacklisted(userId)?
BL --> TCM: false

TCM -> DB: FindUser(EntraObjectId)
DB --> TCM: User { Id, IsActive=true }

TCM -> TCM: Check User.IsActive == true

TCM -> DB: GetActiveOrgMembership(userId, orgHeader?)
DB --> TCM: UserOrganization { OrgId, IsActive=true }

TCM -> DB: GetOrganization(orgId)
DB --> TCM: Organization { IsActive=true }

TCM -> Ctx: Set(orgId, userId, role)
TCM -> Ctrl: next()

== Failure: No Org Claim / Unknown User ==

Req -> JWT: Authorization: Bearer <token>
JWT -> TCM: Authenticated user (no Entra match)

TCM -> DB: FindUser(EntraObjectId)
DB --> TCM: null

TCM --> Req: **403 Forbidden**\n"User not found in system"

== Failure: Deactivated User (Blacklisted) ==

Req -> JWT: Authorization: Bearer <token>
JWT -> TCM: Authenticated user

TCM -> BL: IsBlacklisted(userId)?
BL --> TCM: **true**

TCM --> Req: **403 Forbidden**\n"Account deactivated"

== Failure: Inactive Organization ==

Req -> JWT: Authorization: Bearer <token>
JWT -> TCM: Authenticated user

TCM -> BL: IsBlacklisted(userId)?
BL --> TCM: false
TCM -> DB: FindUser
DB --> TCM: User (active)
TCM -> DB: GetOrganization(orgId)
DB --> TCM: Organization { IsActive=**false** }

TCM --> Req: **403 Forbidden**\n"Organization inactive"

@enduml
